data.description: Here is a rare find! Ready to move in updated 3/2 home in a nice low traffic quiet subdivision located in Flood Zone X (DID NOT flood in 2016!) This home features: a new roof (2 yrs old), updated kitchen with granite countertop and new stainless steel appliances, updated bathrooms, freshly painted inside and out, cathedral ceiling with wood beam in the living room, wood burning fireplace, minutes away from Acadiana Mall, restaurants, hospital, library, shopping and entertainment. Relax in the spacious back yard with beautiful rose bushes and citrus trees. RD eligiblile.
